oji\" />  以為普通爆擦<br />\n<br />\n以前都爆撚到見到紅肉，好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e2365b747d539358693bbf832a271de33fecca","tid":260753,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過一樣情況<br />\n我嗰陣係查啲蛾羅立英之後帶布手套&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇好返？</blockquote><br />\n有好返，但無記錯都要一兩個月時間<br />\n呢段期間出街最好都帶手套啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0302a38d643ec8604263decfbb6b315934888a","tid":260753,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"Krocodil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5729ce087db3d9981946b0cf21c64c7f73ff92","tid":260753,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，一樣，我有一隻手指頭同掌心都係咁，我以為係主婦手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過去濕潤既地方就唔會咁乾<br />\n<br />\n冇睇醫生，都係keep 住搽cream / 蛾羅納笑 / 死海鹽<br />\n<br />\n隻手臂就咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  埋唔到口 一撻撻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/100625_fa4f4cc24fe2e6326a06834066d488a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F100625_fa4f4cc24fe2e6326a06834066d488a9.jpg&h=2b28539d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/100632_6a6e189064aac16b726375658000b13d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F100632_6a6e189064aac16b726375658000b13d.jpg&h=f29a5aa0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n係未皮膚病呀，咁都唔睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}